Changelog

Unreleased
- Added rc/ upstream C source and documentation for reference.
- Reworked parser/lexer toward rc grammar and tokenization; expanded AST kinds.
- Added rc-style expansion features (free carets, $ifs, $#, $^, $", backquotes).
- Added control-flow and function plan support with dynamic scoping.
- Added job tracking plus jobs/fg/bg/apid builtins.
- Added ParseAll and multi-line parsing support.
- Converted docs to plaintext and added LICENSE from rc/COPYING.
- Cleaned up unused generated artifacts.
